values.comment:
Convert a `Vec2` to a `Point2d`.

   Point2d.fromVec2 (vec2 2 3)
   --> Point2d.unsafe { x = 2, y = 3 }

Convert a `Vec3` to a `Point3d`.

   Point3d.fromVec3 (vec3 2 1 3)
   --> Point3d.unsafe { x = 2, y = 1, z = 3 }

Convert a `Vec2` to a `Vector2d`.

   Vector2d.fromVec2 (vec2 2 3)
   --> Vector2d.unsafe { x = 2, y = 3 }

Convert a `Vec3` to a `Vector3d`.

   Vector3d.fromVec3 (Vector3.vec3 2 1 3)
   --> Vector3d.unsafe { x = 2, y = 1, z = 3 }
